    "synopsis": "D'onne Ulanti, now feared across the Underhive as Mad Donna, drags a Spire-born past behind every knife stroke. When a Guilder hints that he knows why she fell from noble society into Hive Primus, Donna and her House Escher allies are pulled into a trap of secrets, murder and betrayal. Flashbacks rebuild the life she lost while the present-day hunt strips away any illusion that the Underhive has made her simpler. A female-led Necromunda revenge-survival story with courtly trauma curdled into gang violence.",
